45__RCSID("$NetBSD: openpam_static.c,v 1.3 2017/05/06 19:50:09 christos Exp $");
46
47#include <string.h>
48
49#include <security/pam_appl.h>
50
51#include "openpam_impl.h"
52
53#ifdef OPENPAM_STATIC_MODULES
54
55SET_DECLARE(openpam_static_modules, pam_module_t);
56
57/*
58 * OpenPAM internal
59 *
60 * Locate a statically linked module
61 */
62
63pam_module_t *
64openpam_static(const char *path)
65{
66 pam_module_t * const *module;
67
68 SET_FOREACH(module, openpam_static_modules) {
69 if (strcmp((*module)->path, path) == 0)
70 return (*module);
71 }
72 return (NULL);
73}
74
75#endif /* OPENPAM_STATIC_MODULES */
